Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的生命已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的新生命怎么使用由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ  这回是什么星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这家伙干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿上战斗服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先穿上再说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开始传送  之后是战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和你打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是GANTZ的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个正常不过的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑  GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就是  这个就是GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是它的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野星人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们挺走运的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经死过一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪打我们的黑超也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们从这里回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以重新开始人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之前把他们全都杀了也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不能死两次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那六个人都杀掉\N（穿上它会使能力大幅提升）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是七个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋  总是把累活推给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是摆脱你的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你这个杀人狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你还没成年  我才利用你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为自己多了不起  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  再多演一会儿戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他听我们的会方便多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受杀人是随时随地都有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对演技可是很有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说为了我们能活着回原来的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要和你战斗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的照片么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了  这个是GANTZ的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野GANTZ是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个...黑球...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还没有成年呀  我们要合起来杀死他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大人的话你就动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们谈出结果了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是理不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们不如这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让玄野给我们看证据
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明给我们看  让我们可以完全相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有什么意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才不是看到紧身衣的威力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是什么魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让我们能够相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加...加藤...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小计
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岸本  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在给我看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈又是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能追到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来啊  你这个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饶不了你  我绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没有爆炸时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚...刚才是那是...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定、一定是他的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里死掉的朋友在被人打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会不会就是想要我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里一定有原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪打出去也没有延迟爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦让你给我们看证据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你突然朝我们开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我们怎么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能现在肯定他是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家说怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得他的话好像...不怎么可信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说什么杀不杀他之类难听的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如想想我们自己怎么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我无法相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是危及我们的生命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信一个乱开喷子的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚才看到了那件衣服的确很神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了预防万一  我们穿上它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他  我们要严密监视  大家觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请快去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看着他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不要忘记拿上枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手  我不会再向你们开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轻信你的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是向我们开枪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请去换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里出去就是正门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个女人一起换
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是玄野的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我是他的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是死了的教师是管不住学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不打算用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防身还是拿着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  如果他没说假话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一步我们该会被传送到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想搞什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像这楼有10层
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1层的洋式居酒屋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2层到最顶全是服务业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解得很清楚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...  浦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪被他抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么吃的  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把枪给我  玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有想把你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有什么可说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不相信  你们都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.30,0:11:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先放下枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才能心平气和地说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是做说服工作的时候呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不见他手里的枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是一枪下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不想看着年纪轻轻的走上歧路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是美好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来商量怎么办...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们才是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们用棒子把流浪汉活活打死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻里不是放过被破坏的寺院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺院？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就在那里杀了流浪汉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会相信他说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  准备装到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把玄野星人杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了这是GANTZ的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够他了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你到底看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好地自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤  怎么办  谁都不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们要把玄野星人干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们应该就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是...外星人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电梯在往下走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8楼那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去7层
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截断他的退路  不让他活着出这栋楼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GANTZ这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他在上面那层
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只有一个人而我们是七个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一齐进攻就能轻易杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们刚才不是还相信他说的话呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了  他就是那个逼债的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是玄野或GANTZ制造的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  让我快点回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说很喜欢这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有必要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古田先生  你不想活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两码子事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们还不知道他是不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得把他...还是你有别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是玄野的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我是他班主任又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  没有必要非得杀掉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该想想还有没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就敢打包票吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都死了还能追究你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想开枪的话  就请你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们几个去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够黑啊  GANTZ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  虽然我跟无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有什么可说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再惺惺作态了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最坏的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命  他要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢动一步老师就开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么  快把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来  玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果杀了你就能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要向我开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有什么办法想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让开  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  这样你还反抗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓人质？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦先生  你这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又不是外星人  放开她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还得把玄野星人杀掉的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好出此下策
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野同学  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再反抗  受伤的可就是她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴  除了这个就想不出别的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再反抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不反抗  我就不会伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再逼大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都如同纯洁无暇的婴儿一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便遭遇困苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要放弃，勇敢向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在雨中我的心因往事而作痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤寂的我犹如一块浮冰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲吻我纤弱的手指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这使我记起你的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.13,0:22:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便现在一切都结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的那个吻我永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的吻，永不会忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.96,0:22:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就象是迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.99,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦身陷其中  就很难找到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  没有出不去的迷宫
